text: Sultan Duzelbayev (born 12 March 1994) is a male Kazakh recurve archer from Almaty. He competed in the archery competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Kazakhstani male archers Category:Living people Category:1994 births Category:Sportspeople from Almaty Category:Archers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic archers of Kazakhstan Category:Archers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Kazakhstan
